        Ashna Ashok, the primary members of Teudu's development team
        from 2012 onward. We also can't wait to include a running list
        of names for everyone who has contributed to Teudu, not just
        on the web app but also the Kinect, Android, and iOS apps. An
        automated way of fetching this list is coming soon!
      </p>
      <p class="event-modal-text-regular">
        Teudu is maintained exclusively by the ACM Apps Team.
        To learn more about ACM at CMU, visit our website at
        <a href="http://acmatcmu.org/">
          http://acmatcmu.org/
        </a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

